{
  "id": "5acb77fd4709b300143f23a3",
  "title": "Cobb-Douglas utility curve",
  "created": 1523284022,
  "updated": 1541147398,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5acb77fd4709b300143f23a3",
      "text": "Cobb-Douglas utility curve",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523284022,
      "updated": 1523284022
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb7835aff09e00003eebfa",
      "text": " [$ u(x, y) = x^a y^{1-a}]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523284022,
      "updated": 1523284066
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb78f0aff09e00003eec03",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/521e0cd7678cd89b730437b2e54cfcad] ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523284208,
      "updated": 1523285980
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb7fdcaff09e00003eec08",
      "text": "  [src http://www.econport.org/econport/request?page=man_consumer_demand]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523285980,
      "updated": 1523285981
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb7923aff09e00003eec04",
      "text": " 図はa=0.5の時、[$ u(x, y) = x^{0.5} y^{0.5}]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523284260,
      "updated": 1523284289
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb7941aff09e00003eec05",
      "text": " これはx,yそれぞれ対数を取れば単なる重み付平均である",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523284290,
      "updated": 1526021331
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb79a2aff09e00003eec07",
      "text": " \tつまり、片方の財の[効用]はその量の対数に比例する、ということ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523284387,
      "updated": 1541147398
    },
    {
      "id": "5af53cd6aff09e0000eac194",
      "text": "  \t[限界効用逓減の法則]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1526021335,
      "updated": 1526021342
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb7987aff09e00003eec06",
      "text": " 一方で[予算制約線]は対数を取らないこの空間上で直線になる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523284360,
      "updated": 1523284437
    },
    {
      "id": "5af54a87aff09e0000eac195",
      "text": "  Cobb, C. W., & Douglas, P. H. (1928). A theory of production. The American Economic Review, 18(1), 139-165.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1526024839,
      "updated": 1526024945
    },
    {
      "id": "5af54a87aff09e0000eac196",
      "text": "  ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1526024839,
      "updated": 1526024842
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb785faff09e00003eebfc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523284063,
      "updated": 1523284260
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb7836aff09e00003eebfb",
      "text": "Constant Elasticity of Substitution (CES) utility function",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523284023,
      "updated": 1523284064
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb7860aff09e00003eebfe",
      "text": "\t[$ u(x, y) = (a x ^ r + b y ^ r) ^ {1/r}]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523284064,
      "updated": 1523284107
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb788faff09e00003eebff",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523284112,
      "updated": 1523284112
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb785faff09e00003eebfd",
      "text": "quadratic",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523284064,
      "updated": 1523284141
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb78acaff09e00003eec01",
      "text": "\t[$ u(x, y) = 2 a x - (b - y)^2]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523284141,
      "updated": 1523284166
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb78c2aff09e00003eec02",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523284163,
      "updated": 1523284163
    }
  ]
}